LUXEMBOURGISH CITIZENSHIP

   PUB_LUX_NAT_octobre2019_WEBSITE

   inlingua® Luxembourg is registered to the
   Ministry of the national Education of the childhood and youth
   and propose one-to-one and group courses
   to obtain the Luxembourgish citizenship

 Language Courses in Luxembourg with inlingua®

A specialist in providing language courses in the Grand Duchy, for more than
20 years, our language school offers you made-to-measure courses
in Luxembourg and Esch-sur-Alzette. Come and find out about our language
lessons in Luxembourgish, German, English and many others.

   Our two language schools, situated in Luxembourg and Esch-sur-Alzette,
   are part of the inlingua^® international network. Our way of working,
   the inlingua^®^   method, is used in more than 350 centres across 40
   countries and allows us to profit from the pedagogical resources of our
   network and therefore to offer high quality language training.

   Each request for training is handled efficiently, and follows a
   strictly designed procedure created to ensure that you reach your
   objective. Our courses allow each student to make progress in their
   chosen language, and to measure their progress using the Cadre européen
   commun de référence pour les langues (CECR).

   We offer :
     * Language courses for businesses (at our school or your premises)
     * Language courses for adults (individual or group training)
     * Language courses for children (All-year-round, or intensive courses
       during school holidays)
     * Language coaching (with a personalised programme) weekly or à la
       carte.
     * Preparation for, and and sitting of, international exams (TEF,
       TEFAQ, BULATS, TOEIC, etc

   IFRAME: https://player.vimeo.com/video/156576269

